OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunny spells as showers clear away
OL,7,Fthis evening. The rest of the night
OL,8,Fwill see mostly dry conditions,
OL,9,Fperhaps the odd light shower for
OL,10,FArgyll.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FFairly cloudy but dry for most
OL,13,Fplaces. The best of the sunnier spells
OL,14,Fare expected early in the morning and
OL,15,Flate in the day.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FRather
OL,18,Fcloudy on Monday with a few showery
OL,19,Foutbreaks of rain spreading south.
OL,20,FMainly dry and bright on Tuesday and
OL,21,FWednesday with some sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
